---
title: Slack 模块交互流程图
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Slack User
    participant Slack as Slack API
    participant Adapter as adapter.go
    participant Handler as 事件处理器
    participant Builder as builder.go
    participant Formatter as formatting.go
    participant Chunker as chunker.go
    participant Security as security.go
    participant Validator as validator.go
    participant Engine as Engine

    Note over User,Slack: 外部交互层

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,Slack: 1. Slash Command 流程
        User->>Slack: /hotplex reset
        Slack->>Adapter: HTTP POST /slack
        Adapter->>Security: VerifySignature()
        Security-->>Adapter: 验证结果

        alt 验证失败
            Adapter-->>Slack: 401 Unauthorized
        else 验证成功
            Adapter->>Handler: handleSlashCommand()
            Handler->>Handler: CheckRateLimit()
            Handler->>Builder: BuildPermissionRequest()
            Builder->>Formatter: MrkdwnFormatter.Format()
            Formatter-->>Builder: mrkdwn 文本
            Builder-->>Handler: slack.Block
            Handler->>Chunker: ChunkMessage()
            Chunker-->>Handler: 分块消息
            Handler->>Validator: ValidateBlocks()
            Validator-->>Handler: 验证结果
            Handler->>Slack: PostMessage
            Slack-->>User: 权限请求消息
        end
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over User,Slack: 2. Event 流程 (App Mention)
        Slack->>Adapter: HTTP POST /events
        Adapter->>Security: VerifySignature()
        Security-->>Adapter: 验证结果

        alt 验证失败
            Adapter-->>Slack: 401 Unauthorized
        else 验证成功
            Adapter->>Handler: handleEvent()
            Handler->>Handler: 解析 event payload
            Handler->>Engine: ExecuteCommand()
            Engine-->>Handler: 执行结果
            Handler->>Builder: BuildAnswerMessage()
            Builder->>Formatter: MrkdwnFormatter.Format()
            Formatter-->>Builder: mrkdwn 文本
            Builder-->>Handler: slack.Block
            Handler->>Chunker: ChunkMessage()
            Chunker-->>Handler: 分块消息
            Handler->>Validator: ValidateBlocks()
            Validator-->>Handler: 验证结果
            Handler->>Slack: UpdateMessage
            Slack-->>User: 响应消息
        end
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over User,Slack: 3. Interactive 流程 (Button Click)
        User->>Slack: 点击按钮
        Slack->>Adapter: HTTP POST /interactive
        Adapter->>Security: VerifySignature()
        Security-->>Adapter: 验证结果

        alt 验证失败
            Adapter-->>Slack: 401 Unauthorized
        else 验证成功
            Adapter->>Handler: handleInteractive()
            Handler->>Handler: 解析 callback_id
            alt callback_id = "approve"
                Handler->>Handler: HandleApprove()
                Handler->>Engine: ResumeSession()
                Engine-->>Handler: 会话恢复
            else callback_id = "deny"
                Handler->>Handler: HandleDeny()
            end
            Handler->>Builder: BuildApprovedMessage() / BuildDeniedMessage()
            Builder-->>Handler: slack.Block
            Handler->>Slack: UpdateMessage
            Slack-->>User: 结果消息
        end
    end

    Note over User,Slack: 核心文件职责

